title: GarageBOSS 7 Quart Oil Drain Pan with Funnel
features: Integrated, wide mouth funnel for quick and clean fluid draining
Holds up to 7 quarts of either old oil or anti-freeze
Low profile to fit under the lowest cars

description: Responsible disposal of your old oil starts here. Drain, transport & recycle your old oil with no mess or hassle. The GarageBOSS 7 quart recycle drain pan allows you to drain directly into the transporting container so you can transport your used oil or anti-freeze in the most efficient manner with the least amount of mess. Designed with an integrated, wide mouth funnel, draining fluids has never been easier or cleaner. Just drain, seal & transport to your nearest oil recycling center or retailer. The 7 quart recycle drain pan is shallow enough to fit under your vehicle & is designed with built in handle for easy carrying. The rectangular design allows you to lay the pan flat for transport & the durable construction makes this a product you cancount on for years to come.
